parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle's brakes lock up
the vehicle surges forward or backward
the brakes make a loud noise
the brakes slip before coming to a complete stop
the brake pedal goes to the floor
the vehicle takes an extended distance to stop
the ABS warning light appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of brake components can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brakes make a loud noise
the brakes slip before coming to a complete stop
the vehicle takes an extended distance to stop
the brake pads and shoes fail
the brake calipers fail
the brake modulation valve fails
the rotors fail.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective horn button can cause difficulty in alerting other motorists of the vehicle's presence, leading to potential accidents.
symptoms: The horn button is hard to locate
especially in emergency situations
and may not function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause fires, stalling, and loss of power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Fires in the engine compartment
stalling
loss of power
smoke emanating from the steering column
and blown fuses.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rearview Mirror and Interior Lighting Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to adjust the rearview mirror and lack of interior lighting can reduce visibility, leading to accidents or difficulty driving.
symptoms: Difficulty adjusting the rearview mirror
blown fuses
and lack of interior lighting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden unintended acceleration can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities, as well as damage to property.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly accelerates without warning
often when shifting gears
braking
or parking
resulting in loss of control and potential accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cruise control malfunction can cause sudden unintended acceleration, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The cruise control engages or disengages unexpectedly
causing the vehicle to accelerate or decelerate without warning
often resulting in loss of control and potential accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Throttle sticking can cause sudden unintended acceleration, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The throttle sticks or becomes stuck
causing the vehicle to accelerate without warning
often resulting in loss of control and potential accidents.
